<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>JEJU · 3박 4일 — 7.15–7.18</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gowun+Batang:wght@400;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --basalt:#171c22;
  --ink:#232a33;
  --sea:#0e5e6f;
  --sea-deep:#0a3f4b;
  --tangerine:#ef8f2e;
  --foam:#f4f6f5;
  --sand:#efe9dd;
  --line:#d8ddda;
  --d1:#3d7a5c; --d2:#c05f2b; --d3:#0e5e6f; --d4:#6d5a9e;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%}
body{font-family:'IBM Plex Sans KR',sans-serif;background:var(--foam);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.6;word-break:keep-all}
.serif{font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif}
.wrap{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 18px}

/* ───── HERO ───── */
.hero{background:var(--basalt);color:#fff;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:56px 0 0}
.hero .eyebrow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.3em;color:#9fb4b8;text-transform:uppercase}
.hero .eyebrow::before{content:"";width:36px;height:1px;background:var(--tangerine)}
.hero h1{font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:clamp(40px,11vw,64px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.14;margin:18px 0 10px;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--tangerine)}
.hero .sub{font-size:14.5px;color:#b7c4c6;font-weight:300}
.tickets{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:12px;margin-top:32px}
.ticket{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px;position:relative}
.ticket small{display:block;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--tangerine);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px}
.ticket .rt{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.ticket .ap b{display:block;font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:23px;font-weight:700}
.ticket .ap span{font-size:11.5px;color:#9fb4b8}
.ticket .ap:last-child{text-align:right}
.ticket .mid{flex:1;margin:0 14px;border-top:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,.3);position:relative}
.ticket .mid::after{content:"✈";position:absolute;top:-9px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);font-size:12px;color:#9fb4b8}
.ticket .tm{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:8px;font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600}
.ticket .tm i{font-style:normal;font-size:10.5px;color:#8ba0a4;margin-left:4px;font-weight:400}
.hero-meta{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;margin-top:32px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14)}
.hero-meta div{padding:14px 4px 18px;border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14)}
.hero-meta div:nth-child(2n){border-right:none;padding-left:16px}
.hero-meta div:nth-child(n+3){border-bottom:none}
.hero-meta small{display:block;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8ba0a4;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px}
.hero-meta b{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600}
.wave{display:block;width:100%;height:48px;margin-top:-1px}

/* ───── TABS ───── */
.tabs-wrap{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:60;background:rgba(244,246,245,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.tabs{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:7px;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:10px 14px}
.tab{font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;padding:9px 6px;text-align:center;transition:all .15s;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.tab small{display:block;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;color:#98a19b}
.tab b{font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
.tab.on{background:var(--tc);border-color:var(--tc)}
.tab.on small{color:rgba(255,255,255,.72)}
.tab.on b{color:#fff}

/* ───── PANELS ───── */
main{padding:30px 0 20px}
.panel{display:none;animation:fade .3s ease}
.panel.on{display:block}
@keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.day-head{margin-bottom:8px;padding-bottom:16px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink)}
.day-head small{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.26em;color:var(--dc);margin-bottom:6px}
.day-head h2{font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:clamp(23px,6vw,30px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.25}
.day-head p{font-size:13.5px;color:#68727c;margin-top:5px;font-weight:300}
.day-sum{display:flex;gap:16px;margin:14px 0 18px;font-size:12px;color:#68727c;flex-wrap:wrap}
.day-sum b{color:var(--dc);font-weight:700}

/* ───── MAP (크게, 상단 배치) ───── */
.mapbox{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:16px 12px 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(23,28,34,.07);margin-bottom:28px}
.mapbox h5{font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;padding:0 6px}
.mapbox .mcap{font-size:11.5px;color:#98a1a9;margin:2px 0 8px;padding:0 6px}
.mapbox svg{width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:12px}
.mlegend{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px 14px;margin-top:12px;padding:12px 6px 4px;border-top:1px dashed var(--line)}
.mlegend span{font-size:11px;color:#5b656f;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;line-height:1.3}
.mlegend i{font-style:normal;flex:none;width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--dc);color:#fff;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}

/* ───── TIMELINE ───── */
.tl{position:relative}
.tl::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:6px;top:8px;bottom:8px;width:2px;background:var(--dc);opacity:.22}
.stop{position:relative;margin-bottom:8px}
.stop::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:1px;top:24px;width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;border:3px solid var(--dc);z-index:1}
.stop .time{display:block;margin:0 0 5px 26px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dc);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:18px 20px;margin-left:26px}
.card .tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--dc);border:1px solid currentColor;border-radius:99px;padding:2px 10px;margin-bottom:8px}
.card h3{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.01em;line-height:1.35}
.card h3 .mno{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:21px;height:21px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--dc);color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;vertical-align:2px;margin-right:7px}
.card .addr{font-size:12px;color:#8b949c;margin-top:3px}
.card .desc{font-size:13.5px;color:#4a545e;margin-top:9px;font-weight:300}
.near{margin-top:11px;padding-top:11px;border-top:1px dashed #e6e9e7;font-size:11.5px;color:#8b949c;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;align-items:center}
.near em{font-style:normal;font-weight:700;color:var(--dc);letter-spacing:.08em;font-size:10px;margin-right:2px}
.near span{background:#f2f4f3;border-radius:7px;padding:2px 9px;color:#5b656f;font-weight:500}
.card .nlink{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;margin-top:13px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;background:#03c75a;padding:10px 0;border-radius:11px;width:100%;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.card .nlink::before{content:"N";display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:17px;height:17px;background:#fff;color:#03c75a;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;border-radius:4px}
.card.dark{background:var(--basalt);border-color:var(--basalt);color:#fff}
.card.dark .addr{color:#9aa4b2}.card.dark .desc{color:#c3cad4}
.move{padding:9px 0 13px 26px;font-size:12px;color:#98a1a9;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.move::before{content:"↓";color:var(--dc);font-weight:700}
.move b{color:#5b656f;font-weight:600}
.km{display:inline-block;background:#eceeed;border-radius:6px;padding:1px 8px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#5b656f}
.or{display:inline-block;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;color:#98a1a9;background:#f0f2f1;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;vertical-align:3px;margin:0 4px}

/* ───── STAY / TIPS / FOOTER ───── */
.stay{background:var(--basalt);color:#fff;border-radius:18px;padding:26px 24px;margin:52px 0 20px}
.stay small{display:block;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.26em;color:#9fb4b8;margin-bottom:6px}
.stay b{font-size:17px;font-weight:600}
.stay p{font-size:13px;color:#aebcbf;margin-top:7px;font-weight:300}
.tips{background:var(--sand);border-radius:18px;padding:26px 24px;margin-bottom:52px}
.tips h4{font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:19px;margin-bottom:12px}
.tips li{list-style:none;font-size:13.5px;padding:8px 0 8px 24px;position:relative;color:#4a545e;font-weight:300;border-bottom:1px dashed #d5cbb8}
.tips li:last-child{border:none}
.tips li::before{content:"◦";position:absolute;left:5px;color:var(--tangerine);font-weight:700}
footer{background:var(--basalt);color:#75838a;text-align:center;padding:30px 20px calc(30px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));font-size:11.5px;letter-spacing:.14em}
footer b{color:#c8d2d4;font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif;font-size:13.5px;letter-spacing:.3em;display:block;margin-bottom:5px}

/* 데스크톱 보정 */
@media(min-width:721px){
  .tickets{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .hero-meta{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
  .hero-meta div{border-bottom:none;padding-left:16px}
  .hero-meta div:first-child{padding-left:4px}
  .card .nlink{width:auto;padding:9px 22px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">Jeju Island · 3N4D</div>
    <h1>바람의 섬,<br><em>나흘</em>의 기록</h1>
    <p class="sub">공항에서 가까운 서쪽부터 남쪽을 지나 동쪽 끝까지 — 거리 순으로 설계한 무손실 동선.</p>
    <div class="tickets">
      <div class="ticket">
        <small>OUTBOUND · 7/15 WED</small>
        <div class="rt"><div class="ap"><b>SEL</b><span>서울</span></div><div class="mid"></div><div class="ap"><b>CJU</b><span>제주</span></div></div>
        <div class="tm"><span>09:45<i>출발</i></span><span>11:00<i>도착</i></span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ticket">
        <small>INBOUND · 7/18 SAT</small>
        <div class="rt"><div class="ap"><b>CJU</b><span>제주</span></div><div class="mid"></div><div class="ap"><b>SEL</b><span>서울</span></div></div>
        <div class="tm"><span>13:15<i>출발</i></span><span>14:35<i>도착</i></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div><small>Base</small><b>안덕면 서광리</b></div>
      <div><small>Direction</small><b>서 → 남 → 동</b></div>
      <div><small>First Leg</small><b>공항→협재 40분</b></div>
      <div><small>Stops</small><b>17곳 · 맛집 5</b></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <svg class="wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 48" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,26 C240,48 480,6 720,24 C960,42 1200,12 1440,32 L1440,48 L0,48 Z" fill="#f4f6f5"/></svg>
</section>

<!-- TABS -->
<nav class="tabs-wrap">
  <div class="tabs">
    <button class="tab on" style="--tc:var(--d1)" data-p="p1"><small>7/15 수</small><b>서부</b></button>
    <button class="tab" style="--tc:var(--d2)" data-p="p2"><small>7/16 목</small><b>남부</b></button>
    <button class="tab" style="--tc:var(--d3)" data-p="p3"><small>7/17 금</small><b>동부</b></button>
    <button class="tab" style="--tc:var(--d4)" data-p="p4"><small>7/18 토</small><b>귀가</b></button>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="wrap">

<!-- ═══ DAY 1 ═══ -->
<section class="panel on" id="p1" style="--dc:var(--d1)">
  <div class="day-head">
    <small>DAY 01 · 7/15 WED</small>
    <h2>가장 가까운 바다부터</h2>
    <p>공항 → 협재 → 한림 → 금오름 → 숙소</p>
  </div>
  <div class="day-sum"><span>이동 <b>57km</b></span><span>운전 <b>1시간 10분</b></span><span>공항→첫 코스 <b>40분</b></span></div>
  <div class="mapbox" data-day="1"></div>

  <div class="tl">
    <div class="stop"><span class="time">11:00</span>
      <div class="card dark"><span class="tag" style="color:var(--tangerine)">ARRIVAL</span>
        <h3>제주공항 도착 · 렌터카 수령</h3>
        <div class="addr">11:00 착륙 → 셔틀 + 수령 약 30분</div>
        <p class="desc">11:30 출발. 평화로를 타고 곧장 서쪽으로.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="move"><b>차량 40분</b><span class="km">33km</span> 평화로 → 한림</div>

    <div class="stop"><span class="time">12:20</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">LUNCH</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">1</span>제갈양 제주협재점</h3>
        <div class="addr">제주시 한림읍 한림로 155</div>
        <p class="desc">첫 끼는 숯불 양갈비. 12시대 도착이라 웨이팅 전 입장 확률 높음.</p>
        <div class="near"><em>주변</em><span>협재해변 도보 5분</span><span>옹포리 카페거리</span></div>
        <a class="nlink" href="https://naver.me/FjmHy8ck" target="_blank">네이버지도 열기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="move"><b>도보 5분</b><span class="km">0.5km</span></div>

    <div class="stop"><span class="time">13:40</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">BEACH</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">2</span>협재해수욕장</h3>
        <div class="addr">비양도 전망 · 7월 물빛 절정</div>
        <p class="desc">에메랄드 바다에서 물놀이 or 해변 산책. 오후의 가장 밝은 빛.</p>
        <div class="near"><em>주변</em><span>금능해변 도보 10분</span><span>비양도 도항선</span><span>협재 카페거리</span></div>
        <a class="nlink" href="https://map.naver.com/p/search/%ED%98%91%EC%9E%AC%ED%95%B4%EC%88%98%EC%9A%95%EC%9E%A5" target="_blank">네이버지도 열기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="move"><b>도보 2분</b><span class="km">0.5km</span> 바로 옆</div>

    <div class="stop"><span class="time">15:30</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">PARK</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">3</span>한림공원</h3>
        <div class="addr">협재굴 · 쌍용굴 · 야자수길</div>
        <p class="desc">용암동굴은 여름에도 시원하다. 더위 피난처 겸 관람 1시간 30분.</p>
        <div class="near"><em>주변</em><span>협재굴·쌍용굴 (원내)</span><span>금능석물원</span></div>
        <a class="nlink" href="https://map.naver.com/p/search/%ED%95%9C%EB%A6%BC%EA%B3%B5%EC%9B%90" target="_blank">네이버지도 열기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="move"><b>차량 14분</b><span class="km">10km</span></div>

    <div class="stop"><span class="time">17:30</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">SUNSET</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">4</span>금오름</h3>
        <div class="addr">왕복 40분 등반 · 분화구 능선</div>
        <p class="desc">제주 서부 최고의 노을 명소. 정상에서 협재 바다와 한라산이 동시에.</p>
        <div class="near"><em>주변</em><span>성이시돌목장 우유부단</span><span>새별오름 15분</span><span>저지문화예술인마을</span></div>
        <a class="nlink" href="https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EA%B8%88%EC%98%A4%EB%A6%84" target="_blank">네이버지도 열기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="move"><b>차량 9분</b><span class="km">6km</span> 숙소 방면</div>

    <div class="stop"><span class="time">19:00</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">CHECK-IN</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">5</span>숙소 체크인 · 저녁</h3>
        <div class="addr">안덕면 서광리 산 24 · 금오름에서 10분</div>
        <p class="desc">저녁은 숙소 인근 로컬 식당. 첫날부터 무리 없는 마무리.</p>
        <div class="near"><em>주변</em><span>오설록 3분</span><span>저지리 맛집</span><span>신화월드 10분</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ DAY 2 ═══ -->
<section class="panel" id="p2" style="--dc:var(--d2)">
  <div class="day-head">
    <small>DAY 02 · 7/16 THU</small>
    <h2>차밭과 절벽, 남쪽의 정취</h2>
    <p>오설록 → 카멜리아힐 → 중문 → 1100도로</p>
  </div>
  <div class="day-sum"><span>이동 <b>56km</b></span><span>운전 <b>1시간 20분</b></span><span>최장 구간 <b>25분</b></span></div>
  <div class="mapbox" data-day="2"></div>

  <div class="tl">
    <div class="stop"><span class="time">09:30</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">MORNING</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">1</span>오설록 티뮤지엄</h3>
        <div class="addr">숙소에서 3분 · 녹차밭 전경</div>
        <p class="desc">아침의 녹차밭은 한산하다. 그린티 아이스크림과 함께 느긋한 시작.</p>
        <div class="near"><em>주변</em><span>이니스프리 하우스</span><span>제주항공우주박물관</span></div>
        <a class="nlink" href="https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%98%A4%EC%84%A4%EB%A1%9D%ED%8B%B0%EB%AE%A4%EC%A7%80%EC%97%84" target="_blank">네이버지도 열기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="move"><b>차량 14분</b><span class="km">10km</span></div>

    <div class="stop"><span class="time">11:00</span>
      <div class="card"><span class="tag">GARDEN</span>
        <h3><span class="mno">2</span>카멜리아힐</h3>
